Package: flagr
Type: Package
Title: Implementation of Flag Aggregation in Eurostat
Version: 0.2.0
Author: person("Matteo", "Salvati", email = "salvati.matteo@hotmail.fr", role = c("aut", "cre"))
        person("Mátyás", "Mészáros", email = "matyas.meszaros@ec.europa.eu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Mátyás Mészáros <matyas.meszaros@ec.europa.eu>
Description: This package aims at facilitating the aggregations of flags in Eurostat according to the current 
    methodological guidelines for the R environnement. It offers different kind of flag aggregation options at 
    dissemination level for computing the flags for EU or other aggregates.
